---
By: Han-shan Te-Ch'ing
Source:
  ISBN: 978-0861711437
  Locus:
    Page: 119
  Title: The Clouds Should Know Me by Now
---
My body is like deadwood my thoughts are like ashes
ther's snow on my skull and frost on my jaw
I don't disdain the world just because I'm old
dust finds no place to land in my eyes
